name: Spirit Gorgons. Ascension in the Wind
description:
A silhouette rises from the sands, cloaked in a black mantle that unfurls wildly in the breeze.
From the side, her arms reach skyward, calling forth the elements—earth, air, and spirit.
Ancient stones stand silent as witnesses to her ascent,
capturing a moment where movement and myth become one.
This unique 1/1 NFT from the “Rebirth of the Gorgona” series is a testament to power, transformation, and ritual dance.
